name: BITDEFENDER [<%= malwarename %>]
description: Bitdefender alerts for the threats with low severity.
query: class=bitdefender eventtype=new-incident has(malwarename) severity=low NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4

query: class=bitdefender eventtype=new-incident has(malwarename) severity=medium NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4
